OL,3,CMercedes and Porsche cars among those
OL,4,Cabandoned by owners in Guernsey streets
OL,6,F"If we have building works or an
OL,7,Femergency, the other day an ambulance
OL,8,Fcame they had to park in the middle of
OL,9,Fthe road. It's an eyesore, it's bad
OL,10,Ffor tourism. We get buses coming down
OL,11,Ffrom the cruise ships and all they see
OL,12,Fare abandoned cars"
OL,14,FTory Russell Homeowner said: "Just
OL,15,Fover two years ago the constables of
OL,16,FSt Sampson managed to remove more than
OL,17,Fa dozen vehicles from Saltpans that
OL,18,Fhad been left there for more than a
OL,19,Fdecade.
