OL,3,CMercedes and Porsche cars among those
OL,4,Cabandoned by owners in Guernsey streets
OL,6,F"But due to Guernsey law it can be a
OL,7,Flong and difficult process. If the
OL,8,Fowners can't be traced and the vehicle
OL,9,Fis no longer insured they can apply to
OL,10,Fhave it removed. But if it is still
OL,11,Finsured and not obstructing the
OL,12,Fhighway then the police are virtually
OL,13,Fpowerless."
OL,15,FRecently, the Vale Commons Council put
OL,16,F'disposal notices' on 4 cars in one of
OL,17,Fits carparks in the North but may have
OL,18,Fto cover the cost of the removals
OL,19,Fthemselves.
